=== 发售前 ===
在《十字军之王III》官宣后，《[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]》发表了一篇文章，指游戏中的一条短语“{{tsl|en|Deus vult|上帝的旨意}}”——该短语在前几作及宣传片中均有出现——不会出现在本作中，因为该短语遭到了“大量[[極右派|极右翼]]的滥用”<ref name="RPStenthings" />。一些粉丝认为这篇报导十分不中肯，并质疑游戏的{{tsl|en|historicity|历史真实性|历史准确性}}。制作总监法劳斯回应称这篇报导“误解了这个问题”，并称制作组不会对这个短语区别对待<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-10-22-paradox-says-its-yet-to-decide-whether-crusader-kings-3-has-deus-vult |title=Paradox says it's yet to decide whether Crusader Kings 3 has Deus Vult |website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2019-10-23 |access-date=2019-10-23 |first=Wesley |last=Yin-Poole |archive-date=2019-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023172508/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-10-22-paradox-says-its-yet-to-decide-whether-crusader-kings-3-has-deus-vult |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 评分 ===
正式发售前，玩家普遍对《十字军之王III》的评价十分高。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，《十字军之王III》拿到了91/100的分数<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/crusader-kings-iii |title=Crusader Kings III for PC Reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |access-date=2020-09-01 |archive-date=2020-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901133212/https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/crusader-kings-iii |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

另一篇报导指出，“[[IGN|IGN]]给了《十字军之王III》10/10的分数，这是业界给予该作的最高评价，另外PC Gamer和PCgamesN分别给了该作94%的分数和9/10的分数<ref>{{Cite web|last=Jones|first=Gary|date=2020-08-31|title=Crusader Kings 3 release date, launch time news and CK3 review scores|url=https://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/gaming/1329646/Crusader-Kings-3-release-date-time-CK3-review-scores|access-date=2020-09-01|website=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901095358/https://www.express.co.uk/entertainment/gaming/1329646/Crusader-Kings-3-release-date-time-CK3-review-scores|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

